Waktu berlalu, kedamaian di Mars pun berakhir ketika segel kegelapan terbuka sehingga monster turun di permukaan Mars. Persatuan Perdamaian Bumi bergegas mengumpulkan sebuah tim yang dinamakan GUTS-Select. Setelah menemukan cahaya Decker dalam dirinya, Kanata bergabung dalam tim ahli GUTS-Select yang baru direformasi menjadi pasukan Anti-Sphere.

programme.desc: Baek Jong-won will transform into a catering chef with Ahn Bo-hyun, Oh Dae-hwan, and DinDin! Arriving only with backpacks, they have to prepare a large amount of customized food within limited time.

programme.title: Best Of I Can See... S9, Ep 1
programme.desc: I Can See Your Voice is back in Season 9! Join the hosts and special celebrity guests to guess which of the contestants are skilled or tone-deaf just by looking at their appearance!

programme.title: Europe Outside...: Spain, Ep 2
programme.desc: Europe Outside Your Tent returns with a new set of cast members! Jo Jin-Woong, Choi Won-young, Park Myung-hoon and Kwon Yul will go on a camping trip around Spain and enjoy its scenery and nature.

programme.title: Unexpected Business S2, Ep 11
programme.desc: Unexpected Business is back with a new season! Starring Jo In-sung and Cha Tae-hyun, the two city men will run a small shop in a countryside town and share memories with the locals.

programme.title: The Heavenly Idol, Ep 9
programme.desc: While Pontifex Lembrary fights against the devil, he gets transferred to a different world possessing the body of an unpopular idol Woo Yeon-woo! Will he be able to adapt to idol life?

programme.title: The Heavenly Idol, Ep 10
programme.desc: While Pontifex Lembrary fights against the devil, he gets transferred to a different world possessing the body of an unpopular idol Woo Yeon-woo! Will he be able to adapt to idol life?

programme.title: True Beauty, Ep 11
programme.desc: Adapted from the popular webtoon of the same title, 'True Beauty' depicts the romance story of Im Joo-kyeong, who puts on make up all the time to hide her bare face, and two men Lee Soo-ho and Han Seo-joon.

programme.title: Secret Reunion
programme.desc: Two former adversaries (Song Kang-Ho and Kang Dong-Won) cross paths six years after their last confrontation and end up working together in this action blockbuster.

programme.title: Seven Days
programme.desc: When her daughter is kidnapped, a lawyer is forced to defend a convict on death row and win his final appeal to overturn the sentence in seven days.

programme.title: Swing Kids
programme.desc: The story of a North Korean soldier who joined the tap dancing team 'Swing Kids' in the Geoje prison camp during the Korean War.

programme.title: Life Is Beautiful
programme.desc: Se-yeon, devoted her entire life to her family, suddenly learns she is gravely ill. Now she is determined to live for herself more than ever and looks for her first love with the help of her husband.

programme.title: Samjin Company English Class
programme.desc: In the mid-1990s in South Korea, three female office co-workers who enroll in English classes in hopes to advance their careers, struggle to expose the corruption inside their company.

programme.title: The Roundup
programme.desc: 4 years after the events of Garibong district round up operation, Geumcheon Police's Major Crimes Unit is given a mission to repatriate a fugitive who fled to Vietnam.

programme.title: Fist & Furious
programme.desc: A former detective grants permission to a freelance video journalist to cover his revenge journey on a mob boss whom previously killed his partner during an investigation.

programme.title: Honest Candidate 2
programme.desc: Joo Sang-sook, who failed to win the Seoul mayoral election by dropping the truth bomb on national television, is suddenly pulled into the spotlight again after rescuing a young man from drowning.

programme.title: Take Point
programme.desc: An elite mercenary force and his team get caught in the crossfire between the U.S. and China which sparks fear of an impending World War III.

programme.title: The Berlin File
programme.desc: A North Korean agent in Berlin is betrayed and cut loose when a weapons deal is exposed. Together with his wife, they try to escape being purged, while being pursued by some Korean operative.

programme.title: Escape From Mogadishu
programme.desc: Personnel of the North and South Korea embassies must join hands to escape from war-torn Somalia.

programme.title: The Prison
programme.desc: A former detective enters a prison as a convict in order to meet a man who is known as The King among the inmates so he can reveal the truth about his brother's death.

programme.title: A Special Lady
programme.desc: Kisah tentang seorang wanita yang menjadi wakil ketua sebuah organisasi gangster terkemuka, melawan kekejaman para pria demi melindungi putra semata wayangnya.

programme.title: Voice Of A Murderer
programme.desc: Satu-satunya putra dari seorang pembawa berita menghilang tanpa jejak. Seorang polisi veteran dan pasukan khususnya ditugaskan dalam kasus ini, tapi si penculik mengetahui keterlibatan polisi tersebut.

programme.title: Going By The Book
programme.desc: Keadaan menjadi tidak terkendali saat seorang polisi lalu lintas yang taat peraturan dipilih untuk berpura-pura menjadi perampok bank dalam sebuah latihan.

programme.title: Don't Go Too Far
programme.desc: Saat berdebat tentang pembagian warisan ayah mereka, seorang kakak laki-laki tertua menerima panggilan telepon yang menyatakan bahwa putranya telah diculik.

programme.title: The Tooth And The Nail
programme.desc: Berdasarkan novel karya Bill S. Ballinger dengan judul yang sama, film ini menceritakan tentang seorang pesulap yang merencanakan trik paling rumit untuk mengungkap konspirasi tersembunyi di balik kematian tunangannya.

programme.title: Lover's Concerto
programme.desc: Ji-hwan menerima banyak surat cinta tak bernama, yang mengingatkannya pada dua sahabatnya yang pergi lima tahun lalu. Tiga sekawan ini biasa menghabiskan waktu bersama, namun bagaimana jika perasaan cinta muncul?

programme.title: Queen Of Walking
programme.desc: Seorang siswi SMA yang harus berjalan kaki selama empat jam menuju sekolah setiap harinya, secara tak terduga memulai latihannya untuk menjadi atlet jalan cepat.

programme.title: We Are Brothers
programme.desc: Dua kakak beradik yang terpisah sejak lahir bersatu kembali 30 tahun kemudian dan melakukan perjalanan untuk mencari ibu mereka yang menderita Alzheimer.

programme.title: Sunflower
programme.desc: Seorang mantan gangster yang dibebaskan dari penjara ingin menjalani kehidupan nan tenang bersama keluarganya. Namun, niatnya terancam saat seorang politisi mencoba membongkar restoran keluarganya demi membangun mal.

programme.title: A Day
